{"id": 2782, "title": "Ticket #2782: Remove GT4 GRAM support from grid universe", "description": "<blockquote>\nWeb Services GRAM (aka gt4) never saw wide-spread use and is no longer supported by Globus. File transfer for gt4 jobs in Condor broke starting in 7.5.1 and the first complaint arrived over a year and half later (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"abandoned\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=2662\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2662'); return false;\" title=\"Gridftp server in Condor broken\">#2662</a></span>). The jar files for gt4 support take up 30MB, which is almost 20% of Condor's installation size. Linux native packages can't include pre-compiled jar files from third parties (i.e. no jar files that we take from Globus) (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"new\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=2134\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2134'); return false;\" title=\"[Debian] Disable gt gahp for Debian\">#2134</a></span>).\n\n<p>For all of these reasons, we should drop support for gt4 gram in Condor.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Feb-06 15:24</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/03a0f934243ba6163171003d7cfd66dd4b214be8\">[30128]</a></span>: Make index entries appear different for config knobs that are gone due to GT4 support removal ===GT=== <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=2782\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2782'); return false;\" title=\"Remove GT4 GRAM support from grid universe\">#2782</a></span>  (By Karen Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Jan-25 11:35</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/3f40045fbdd2386eb536a5f2c176d4ca78f79e1a\">[29196]</a></span>: Remove mention of GT4 GRAM from the manual. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=2782\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2782'); return false;\" title=\"Remove GT4 GRAM support from grid universe\">#2782</a></span>  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Jan-25 11:35</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/0794b953f0d84347ccd3c03baf59263d745217f6\">[29197]</a></span>: Add version history for dropping gt4 support. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=2782\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2782'); return false;\" title=\"Remove GT4 GRAM support from grid universe\">#2782</a></span> ===VersionHistory:Complete===  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Jan-25 11:35</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/e9a58a288f0bab0835b1fc715be5ec9322e90b54\">[29195]</a></span>: Remove <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=GlobusXml\" title=\"Globus Xml\">GlobusXml</a></span> job attribute. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=2782\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2782'); return false;\" title=\"Remove GT4 GRAM support from grid universe\">#2782</a></span>  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<